# Task Manager REST API

A REST API built with Flask that allows users to manage tasks.

This project demonstrates backend API development using Python.

## Features
- Create tasks
- View tasks
- Update tasks
- Delete tasks

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Flask
- REST API
- JSON

## Installation

Install Flask:

pip install flask

## Usage

Start the server:

python task_api.py

The API will run at:

http://127.0.0.1:5000

## API Endpoints

GET /tasks  
Returns all tasks.

POST /tasks  
Creates a new task.

PUT /tasks/<id>  
Updates task status.

DELETE /tasks/<id>  
Deletes a task.

